### Online MBA vs Regular MBA – Which is Better?
| Aspect | Online MBA | Regular (On‑Campus) MBA |
|---|---|---|
| **Flexibility** | 9/10 – Study from anywhere, self‑paced | 4/10 – Fixed schedule |
| **Cost (₹)** | ₹80‑150 k (often **Cheap Online MBA India**) | ₹300‑600 k |
| **Networking** | Virtual cohorts, global peers | Physical campus, alumni events |
| **Placement Support** | Varies – many schools now have **Online MBA Placement** cells |
| **ROI** | Higher due to lower fees & faster completion |

Overall, **Online MBA vs Distance MBA** shows comparable outcomes, but the former offers modern digital tools and better employer perception.

